snippet.title: 5 Reasons The World Thinks Americans Are Really Weird!

localized.description:
America. You can love it or hate it, but one thing is undeniable -- we have a lot of really weird customs that other cultures don't understand. Check out part 2 of America's weirdest quirks and traditions, plus John and Lissette answer some questions from our TYTU international viewers. Click to tweet: http://ctt.ec/M0D_0

What are some of the weirdest things you don't understand about Americans? Let us know in the comments!

Find out more about this topic here: http://bit.ly/1pdz5tT

Don't forget guys, if you like this video please "Like," "Favorite," and "Share" it with your friends to show your support - it really helps us out! If there's something you'd like to see John or Lisa discuss on the show, tweet us about it! See you tomorrow :)
